Dialogue.Text: It's where I keep all my books!
Hmm... I wonder what I should read next...
I wish I had time to read them all!
I have this book I'm reading about a sailor girl who fights evil by moonlight
This book seems to be about a girl capturing magical cards that she accidentally released
This one is a book about a girl dueling with many people in order to save a certain Rose Bride
In this book, a group of three girls got summoned into a fantasy world to save a princess
